  "texts": [
    "While internal reorganization is underway, with workers reporting new AI-related tasks-especially in workplaces with chatbot initiatives-these changes have not translated into measurable differences in earnings or hours.",
    "Overall, our findings challenge narratives of imminent labor market disruption from Generative AI.",
    "While we capture early impacts, two pieces of evidence suggest the limited labor market effects may persist in the foreseeable future.",
    "First, our dynamic difference-in-differences estimates remain flat throughout the two-year study period.",
    "Second, even among \"AI front-runners\"-workplaces that have adopted the full suite of proactive chatbot initiatives and workers who adopted early, use the tools daily, or report substantial benefits-the results remain null."
  ],
